@38 = ~I never would have thought in my wildest dreams, I'd be traveling with a kobold bard. I didn't realize that was possible, I suppose I should broaden my horizons.~
@39 = ~Deekin is different from the rest of the kobolds. Deekin's dream is to write wonderful stories that will be the bestest in all the realms!~
@40 = ~I can't say I'm not impressed by your willpower, Deekin.~
@41 = ~Your kind isn't known for their intelligence nor their courage to travel the realms in search of the "bestest" story.~
@42 = ~Deekin will try to keep up with noble deeds and will try not to disappoint!~